<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10150378>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Zammara conflutrimacula n. sp.: A, Holotype male habitus; B, holotype male dorsum; C, holotype male timbal; D, holotype male operculum; E, holotype male lateral view of genitalia; F, holotype male posterior view of genitalia; G, holotype male venter on day of capture; H, holotype male dorsum on day of capture. G and H courtesy of Jérémie Lapèze. Scale bar: A, 2 cm; B, 5 mm; C–D, 2 mm; E–F, 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10150378/files/figure.png" ;
